Class ConfiguredObjectRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.configuration.registry.RegistryOfIRegisterables<IConfigurable>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObjectRegistry<IConfigurable>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReusableComponentsRegistry

    public class ConfiguredObjectRegistry
extends RegistryOfIRegisterables<IConfigurable>
    Registry of runtime objects within a Catalys Application. This registry represents the properties of components which have been loaded into runtime.

        public boolean isSessionReloadable(Name sessionName)
        A session is reload-able if all of the following conditions are true: session is disconnected, session is blocked, session is non-active (session manager component is non-active)
